query:
SELECT 
  od.ano,
  od.bimestre_operacional,
  COUNT(*) as total_videoaulas
FROM videoaulas v
LEFT JOIN ofertas_disciplinas od ON v.oferta_disciplina_id = od.id
GROUP BY od.ano, od.bimestre_operacional
ORDER BY od.ano, od.bimestre_operacional;
